description:
Have you ever wanted to sell courses online with a partner?

In this course I discuss everything you need to know about forming joint venture partnerships online.

This course is perfect for those who are looking to form business partnerships, startups, or want to learn more about selling products online with others.

Here is what I cover:

  • How to find Joint Venture Opportunities online
  • How to leverage interviews to start real business relationships
  • What you should be looking for in a business partner
  • How to split revenue with your partners
  • Tools you can use to be more productive in a partnership
  • Lessons I've learned from past partnerships, both the good and the bad

I even include 3 real examples of partnerships I've formed with other online entrepreneurs and cover them in great detail.

If you have ever considered working online with others, this course is exactly what you need!
title: Form Joint Venture Partnerships To Sell Online Courses
